    • Constructor Detail

      • Api

        public Api(ApiCredentials apiCredentials,
   String appName,
   String contactAddress)
        Create a new Api object to interact with the Tienda Nube API. Valid only for one store and for one app.
        Parameters:
        apiCredentials - The ApiCredentials object with the information to access the API. This contains the store id and the access token.
        appName - The name of the application.
        contactAddress - An email or website to contact the application developer.
